Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.01,Dialogue,Credits,0,0,0,,Subtitle-source: Detective Conan - 214 [AZFS][9AFE4475].avi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:07.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song by Rina Aiuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:07.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Koi wa thrill, shock, suspense
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:07.32,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Koi wa Thrill, Shock, Suspense,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:07.32,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Love is a thrill, shock, suspense,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:10.79,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Mienai chikara tayori ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:10.79,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}relying on an invisible strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:18.36,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Kokoro no tobira tozasazu ni tsuyoku... tsuyoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:18.36,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Leaving the door to the heart open, stronger... stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a strong heart and mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's case is about a room full of mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kid with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is... Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.35,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Watashi ga kanjiteita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.35,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:40.09,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Toge okimi ni no onaji
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:40.09,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}this disorder I've been feeling in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:47.06,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}You ni ataeteita no kano shirenakatta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:47.06,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Perhaps you felt the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:53.40,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Nani ni kokoro o itamete nani ni obieteita no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:53.40,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Without knowing what hurt, what did I fear with my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:58.00,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Ki ni ino tomezu motsureteku futari no shinjitsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:58.00,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}The confrontation of our{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} tan{\r}gling truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:01.54,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Mukiau no ga kowakatta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:01.54,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}We feared to face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:11.35,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Mayoi o aoi kaze ni chirasou toshite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:11.35,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Even when I tried to toss my confusion to the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:17.66,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Mo kakaekirezu ni ita yo kono chisana mune ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:17.66,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}I could not hold all of it in this tiny chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:21.26,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Kokoro no tobira tozasazu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:21.26,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Leaving the door to the heart open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:25.80,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Tsugi e to susumu arata na fuan to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:25.80,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Even if you may have to hold the new uncertainties and confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:35.14,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Mayoi o kakaeteshimaisou ni natte mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:35.14,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}That will follow you to the next place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:46.99,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,The Mysterious Retro Room Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:51.16,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Touto Line
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, you have to come with us to Dolphinland!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't like aquatic shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every man dreams to watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.01,0:02:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...horse racing! After I win, I'll buy a special dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't blow all our money there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ok, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what does Naomi want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She says we should hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, such beautiful ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce, are you Mouri Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! I'm your biggest fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori, you are so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are going to Dolphinland's hotel. Where are you going, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:03:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence! I'm going to Dolphinland too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to the horse races?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we're still waiting for someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuniko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I hope you haven't waited long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, another hottie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still have plenty of time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you are late...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were going to take the 1:20 PM train; we still have ten minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the famous detective Mouri Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just ran into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We all went to the same university.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:57.08,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Yamamoto Kuniko (27)\NClothing Designer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had a get-together last week,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but one of our group members was working abroad and couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She arrived yesterday, so the four of us decided to go out for some drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:03.29,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Oobayashi Kaori (27)\NTravel Agent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So another beauty is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed. She was the most popular, a true queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A queen!? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:20.34,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kaneda Kanami (27)\NHousewife
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's already at Dolphinland's hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a well-known children's clothing designer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we have a designer, a travel agent, and a housewife...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,three beautiful and talented ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think he's right about you, Kuniko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true. After all, aren't you opening your own clothing boutique soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More... or less...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm only a housewife...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're a happily married woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! You look so happy and chubby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you know I don't want to be chubby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:08.99,Top Italic,,0,0,0,,Attention! The train to Dolphinland is now arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:13.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go look for this fourth beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The express-train will have us there in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:29.04,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Theme Park Dolphinland
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the Dolphinland hotel over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:36.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They just finished remodeling it last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's done in a retro style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's called the Retro Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Retro Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:56.13,Dialogue Top,Note,0,0,0,,{\fs20}[Note: ryokan is a Japanese-style inn]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the hotel was originally a famous, traditional\Nryokan called Dolphin-Ryokan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So let's go find Naomi's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuniko, what is Naomi's room number?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Room 503.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Room 503?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We arrived at exactly 2 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Naomi is still sleeping when we're ready to go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cannot believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naomi? Naomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the door is unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go in and see if she is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, you can't go in there. You don't know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na-Naomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, stay calm and don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said, "Don't touch anything!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It turned off automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This TV seems to be on a coin-operated timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhum... Ran, call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the body was found by you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and, of course, someone else was here by{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, I'll need to talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well, I will need to question you all\Nas well. Please wait here for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great! I'll be their body guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take charge of these women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:07:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you wish, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhh... yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have you found, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:17.91,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Fujimura Naomi (27)\NChildren's Clothing Designer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was Fujimura Naomi, 27 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was a children's clothing designer working overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, I found this in one of the victim's pockets. It's pepper spray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Pepper spray?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she used to carry it because she lived overseas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There're a lot of sexual predators in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is full of old-style furnishings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because it's called the Retro Room, Inspector.\NIt's a replica of the old ryokan's guest rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why this TV is coin-operated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:09:00.99,Dialogue Top,Note,0,0,0,,{\fs20}[Note: 100 Yen is about $1 USD.]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:09:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can watch one hour for 100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure the TV turned off when you came into the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was 2 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It says here you can only insert one coin at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:16.30,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the TV came on an hour earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between noon and 1 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was attacked right after turning the TV on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, this candy is so weird, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have never seen candies like these!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So many different old candies... I remember them from when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hotel usually leaves them in the room as complimentary snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the killer and the victim were fighting and scattered them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:10:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is even ice cream. Too bad it's already melted...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, this means she was attacked after turning the\NTV on, but before she ate her ice cream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... What types of ice cream bars are in the fridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, these are the ice cream bars inside the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They all look good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like your hypothesis was right, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this ice cream is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim bought it... or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm, what's this? Condensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look over here! It's damp on the table!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damp? Somebody probably just spilled something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you delivered the dry cleaning to the room before 1 PM, is this correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:11:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I didn't enter because of the "Do Not Disturb"\Nsign. I just left it hanging on the doorknob.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice if the door was locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quit being a pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's a good question. Did you notice if it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I didn't try the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! We just found the victim's cellphone under the table!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very good. Can you find her last call?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Check this out, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:43.18,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,November 19th - 1:08 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:43.18,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Yamamoto Kuniko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto Kuniko. She's one of the ladies who discovered the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at that, the victim called her at 1:08 PM, right before the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when we met Yamamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Naomi called saying we should hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was 1:08 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:08.44,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,November 19th - 1:08 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:08.44,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Fujimura Naomi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... Where were you at that moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the station, waiting for the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got together at 1 PM. Kanami joined us about 10 minutes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got on the 1:20 PM train and arrived at the hotel around 1:50 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were outside of Naomi's room at 2 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, these girls have a perfect alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more thing. Could you please describe the\Nroom when you discovered your friend's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a very well thought-out murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my deduction is right, she is the killer, but I don't have any proof yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that? Something plastic in her pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. The culprit still has the evidence on her. This means she did it!
Comment: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:21.68,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Anime Original
Comment: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:21.68,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Original Air Date
Comment: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:21.68,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,November 20th, 2000
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your cooperation. You can leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, I will leave with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On second thought, I don't think we can leave just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, this is clearly a premeditated murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe the criminal is among us. It's one of these ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you say the criminal is one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy lacks tact sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, the pepper spray found in Fujimura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pocket had\Nnot been used. This means she knew her attacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Second, the room key was on the table...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:28.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was a burglar, why not lock the door on the way\Nout? This would delay discovery of the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, if you recall, all of these ladies have\Na perfect alibi — they were with you at 1 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true, although the actual time of\Ndeath was around 12:20 PM, not 1 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:53.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the TV was on. This means a coin was inserted after 1 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:15:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody needs to be here to insert a coin,\Nthey could just use all those candies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Candies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, explain the trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, right now. Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using the ice cream bar and the candy with a string!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's how it works:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, you drape the string candy over the coin slot like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, place the ice cream bar between the\NTV controls and the furniture as a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, put the other end of the string under the ice cream bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have a coin, Ran-neechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put it into the coin slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the coin stays there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After setting this up, the killer left the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over time the ice cream bar melts and falls away, allowing\Nthe thread to slip to the floor and the coin to slip in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to turn on the TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why there was candy near the TV — to hide the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember the{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}nel knob and table were\Ndamp? It was from the ice cream bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, this ice cream bar was a fairly new flavor.\NIt wouldn't be included with this room's selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naomi could have bought it anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but the killer did not lock the room just so this trick would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the killer had locked the door, her friends would not have been\Nable to open the door and watch the TV turn off automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... the trick is meaningless if nobody is here to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the sign on the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit hung out the sign because the room had to be unlocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but nobody was supposed to get in early, or the plan would fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Naomi called me at 1:08 PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's right! If Naomi was killed forty minutes earlier,\Nshe couldn't have made that call, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They have a point, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time of their incoming and outgoing calls matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an easy explanation: the killer used the victim's cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Kuniko was talking with Naomi when—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly. It was impossible for her to talk to Fujimura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto Kuniko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuniko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After committing the murder, you took Fujimura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cellphone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and went to the station to meet Oobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Kaneda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, using the cellphone in your pocket, you called your\Nown phone and pretended to talk with Fujimura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing you had to do was return the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...during the commotion after the body was discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. You still have it with you. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The plastic bag in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You put Fujimura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cellphone in that bag and took it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this true? Check her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me check your pocket, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now hold it up to the light and tell us what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Several fingerprints are visible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and there is a weird vertical pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I must tell you that when I saw your cellphone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I noticed something very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,02058252805
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To call your number, only the center buttons are necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hence the vertical pattern as you dialed through the plastic bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chiba! Bring the victim's cellphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course the plastic bag has my fingerprints; it was in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the victim's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It matches perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could not forgive Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuniko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, Kuniko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After graduation we both sought the recommendation for a job in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was with a well-known company, and Naomi, who was\Nalready good, became a successful designer with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to have been chosen, but Naomi\Nused her feminine charms on the professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know a thing about it until the professor let\Nit slip one time when we were having drinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I thought you were opening your own clothing boutique!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I exaggerated a little. The truth is I was fired from my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because I had a little too much to drink once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn her! I was so angry with her. I felt so humiliated by Naomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she took away my happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:55.13,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Heya no mado no mukou ni hikouki kumo o nazotte
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:55.13,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Beyond the windows I see a trace of clouds made by an airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:22:03.43,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Kyou kenkashita kimi no koto bakari kangaeteta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:22:03.43,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}And realize I can only think about the fight we had today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:13.98,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Sasai na koto de to madotte fuantei de uboubi na
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:13.98,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}I hesitate with every small thing, and I'm unreliable and hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:22.19,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Ano koro no you ni sugu ni denwashite, Warai aetara ii no ni ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:22.19,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Wishing to be able to be like I used to, and call you right away, laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:32.83,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Chika zuite kuru shifuku no toki wa itami o tomonainagara ashi oto tateru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:32.83,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}I can hear the steps of happiness coming closer, bringing pain along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:41.34,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Kangaesugite fukami ni hamaru kimi no soba ni iru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:41.34,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}You are so focused in deep thoughts you don't realize I'm right beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:50.71,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Natsu no maboroshi hitomi tojimete ichiban saishou ni kimi o omoidasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:50.71,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Summer illusions I see, closing my eyes the first one I remember is you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:54.69,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Dakedo kimi to ikiteyukitai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:54.69,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}and it's because I want to live with you by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:23:00.62,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}Tomadoinagara demo ii tsunaida te o hanasanaide ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:23:00.62,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}I don't mind if you hesitate, just never let go of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a great show!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For sure, and we got the best seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose we are really lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are only brats here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, the dolphins will now toss the balls to the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get ready to catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good job! Even they know you, Uncle!
